				"category": "defensive",
				"description": {
					"value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> The cauthooj is the target of a melee Strike and is adjacent to another enemy that is also within the reach of the melee Strike.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The cauthooj nimbly hops aside, redirecting the triggering Strike against the adjacent enemy. The cauthooj Strides up to half its Speed, and this movement does not trigger reactions.</p>",
